room_title: Escape room "Antidote" by Jackson Escape Rooms in Jackson
room_description:
Amidst the chaos of the plague of the undead, your band of survivors have been able to glean enough information from news and rumors to get to deduce the epicenter of the new plague virus.
The world is experiencing the beginnings of what could be a zombie apocalypse — only you know that the team of dark scientists worked out of a now forgotten and abandoned medical laboratory.

You have one hour to find the ingredients in the lab and create the antidote before the zombie horde arrives — before the world’s best hope succumbs to the plague. 

Hopefully the scientific logs are still intact and your team ready to save humanity.
